short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Removes chrome AI suggestion DOM elements (tagged with the class M8OgIe)

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do the new AI suggestions in search results distract you? Do you find them extremely unhelpful and often incorrect? This extension makes them disappear.
